esponding IMF sensitivity. We also\nnote that a clean selection of population III galaxies at z~7-8 can be achieved\nby adding two JWST/MIRI filters to the JWST/NIRCam filter sets usually\ndiscussed in the context of JWST ultra deep fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 May 2011 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Sep 2011 13:15:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
