odeling analysis are furthermore both consistent\nwith the seasonal heating hypothesis used to explain the modulation of 176P's\nactivity. Additional observations are highly encouraged to further characterize\n176P's active behavior as the object approaches perihelion on 2011 July 01.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 May 2011 21:13:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
