copic stresses such as the total stress, the microscopic interparticle\nstresses such as the ones resulting from capillary forces, in order to\ninterpret more precisely the implications of the pore fluid on the mechanical\nbehaviour of granular materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 May 2011 08:37:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-05-06"}
